HEADWORD: Madman
<hw>Mad"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Madmen</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>A man who is mad; lunatic;
